---
import Container from "./Container.astro"
---
<div id="features">
  <Container>
    <div class="md:w-2/3 lg:w-1/2">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="w-8 h-8 text-primary">
        <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M9 4.5a.75.75 0 01.721.544l.813 2.846a3.75 3.75 0 002.576 2.576l2.846.813a.75.75 0 010 1.442l-2.846.813a3.75 3.75 0 00-2.576 2.576l-.813 2.846a.75.75 0 01-1.442 0l-.813-2.846a3.75 3.75 0 00-2.576-2.576l-2.846-.813a.75.75 0 010-1.442l2.846-.813a3.75 3.75 0 002.576-2.576l.813-2.846A.75.75 0 019 4.5zM19.307 12.438a.5.5 0 01.946 0l.283.992a3 3 0 001.779 1.779l.992.283a.5.5 0 010 .946l-.992.283a3 3 0 00-1.779 1.779l-.283.992a.5.5 0 01-.946 0l-.283-.992a3 3 0 00-1.779-1.779l-.992-.283a.5.5 0 010-.946l.992-.283a3 3 0 001.779-1.779l.283-.992z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
      </svg>
      <h2 class="my-8 text-2xl font-bold text-white md:text-4xl">
        Tecnologia d'Avanguardia per il Karaoke Pro.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-400">Platinum Karaoke Pro non è un semplice player, è una stazione di produzione audio e regia mobile completa.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-16 grid divide-x divide-y divide-gray-800 overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border border-gray-800 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 lg:divide-y-0 xl:grid-cols-4">
      
      <!-- AI STEM SEPARATION -->
      <div class="group relative bg-[#0a0a0a] transition hover:z-[1] hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-primary/10">
        <div class="relative space-y-8 p-8">
          <div class="text-5xl">🧠</div>
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <h5 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white transition group-hover:text-[#FF2D55]">AI Stem Separation</h5>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Estrai voce e base da qualsiasi video originale in meno di 60 secondi con la potenza della tua GPU NVIDIA.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- RADAR RMS -->
      <div class="group relative bg-[#0a0a0a] transition hover:z-[1] hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-primary/10">
        <div class="relative space-y-8 p-8">
          <div class="text-5xl">📡</div>
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <h5 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white transition group-hover:text-[#00E5FF]">Radar RMS Anti-Garbage</h5>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Il primo sistema che "ascolta" il video e taglia automaticamente pubblicità e silenzi finali tipici di YouTube.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- SMART BOOKING -->
      <div class="group relative bg-[#0a0a0a] transition hover:z-[1] hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-primary/10">
        <div class="relative space-y-8 p-8">
          <div class="text-5xl">📲</div>
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <h5 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white transition group-hover:text-[#00E676]">Smart Booking QR</h5>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Addio foglietti! I tuoi clienti scansionano il QR Code, sfogliano il catalogo e si prenotano dallo smartphone.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- AUDIO DSP -->
      <div class="group relative bg-[#0a0a0a] transition hover:z-[1] hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-primary/10">
        <div class="relative space-y-8 p-8">
          <div class="text-5xl">🎛️</div>
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <h5 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white transition group-hover:text-[#FFD700]">Rack Audio DSP</h5>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Compressore dinamico e Turbo Boost +6dB. Mantieni un volume di uscita costante e cristallino per tutta la serata.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </Container>
</div>
